OL,6,FThe past is very much in the present
OL,7,Fin our courts.
OL,9,FOn Monday, the families of two men who
OL,10,Fwere murdered by loyalist
OL,11,Fparamilitaries almost 50 years ago
OL,12,Fwere told they were to receive
OL,13,Ffinancial compensation.
OL,15,FJohn Toland and James Loughrey were
OL,16,Fshot in separate incidents in the
OL,17,Fvillages of Eglinton and nearby
OL,18,FGreysteel, County Londonderry, in 1976
OL,19,Fby the UDA.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G1/11
