OL,6,FAn investigation by the now-defunct
OL,7,FHistorical Enquiries Team concluded it
OL,8,Fwas likely there had been collusion
OL,9,Fbetween individual members of the
OL,10,Fsecurity forces and those responsible
OL,11,Ffor murdering Mr Toland in his
OL,12,Fworkplace at the Happy Landing Bar in
OL,13,FEglinton in November 1976.JIt was also
OL,14,Funable to rule out collusion in Mr
OL,15,FLoughrey's killing at his home in
OL,16,FGreysteel the previous week.
OL,18,FOn Monday, the MoD and PSNI settled
OL,19,Fthe cases with no admission of
OL,20,Fliability.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/11
