OL,6,FJames Loughrey's son John said that
OL,7,Fthe families had waited 47 years for
OL,8,Fthis "momentous day."
OL,10,F"My mother was left on her own with
OL,11,Feight children, she was left in that
OL,12,Fsituation by a cruel act where her
OL,13,Fhusband was taken from her.J"Today,
OL,14,Fit's fair to say, brings a degree of
OL,15,Fsatisfaction and vindication after all
OL,16,Fthese years, to see some level of
OL,17,Freparation for the harm that was
OL,18,Fcaused in that act that evening."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/11
