OL,6,FJohn Toland's son Danny said his
OL,7,Ffamily were "delighted" with the
OL,8,Foutcome, and thanked his legal team
OL,9,Fand the Loughrey family, for their
OL,10,Fhelp.
OL,12,FBoth families also reflected on the
OL,13,Ftoll the fight for justice for their
OL,14,Ffathers has taken for them.
OL,16,FDanny Toland said that people had
OL,17,Ftried to take his father's reputation
OL,18,Fas well as his life, by "making out
OL,19,Flies and accusations that were not
OL,20,Ftrue."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/11
