OL,6,F"Something like this carries a legacy
OL,7,Ffrom generation into generation", John
OL,8,FLoughrey added, "for what happened to
OL,9,Fus there's a terrible sense of trauma
OL,10,Fthat manifests in this generation,
OL,11,Fthat never leaves us.
OL,13,F"There's also a terrible sense of
OL,14,Finjustice, that a member of the family
OL,15,Fhas been taken from you and everyone
OL,16,Fknows there's something wrong with
OL,17,Fthat act.
OL,19,F"And there are things that are really
OL,20,Fstill unanswered."
