OL,6,FThe two widows, Mary Loughrey and
OL,7,FMarie Newton, were in Belfast High
OL,8,FCourt on Monday to hear the finding,
OL,9,Fwhere the judge commented on their
OL,10,F"perseverance".
OL,12,FThe sons of Marie and Mary also paid
OL,13,Ftribute to their mothers' strength.
OL,15,FJohn Loughrey remarked that, "our
OL,16,Fperseverance over the years, the way
OL,17,Fwe stuck together as families, the way
OL,18,Fwe supported each other, it shows the
OL,19,Fstrength that people like Mrs Toland
OL,20,Fand my mother have to not let it go
OL,21,Fand pursue it."
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/11
