OL,6,FHe also urged other families to "never
OL,7,Fgive up", saying that while it is a
OL,8,F"long road...it's worth the effort,
OL,9,Fit's worth the journey."
OL,11,FSolicitor for the two families Padraig
OL,12,FO'Muirigh said that more families
OL,13,Fwould be denied the opportunity for
OL,14,Fresolution because of the government's
OL,15,F"draconian" new law dealing with the
OL,16,Flegacy of the Troubles.
