OL,6,F"It is crucial," Mr O'Muirigh added,
OL,7,Fthat cases of this nature are allowed
OL,8,Fto progress through the inquest and
OL,9,Fcivil proceedings unhindered by the NI
OL,10,FTroubles, Legacy and Reconciliation
OL,11,FAct.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately many families will be
OL,14,Fdeprived of the opportunity to pursue
OL,15,Ftheir own legal actions."
OL,17,FThe sons of the two murdered men
OL,18,Fechoed their solicitors remarks
OL,19,Fopposing the legacy act.
