OL,6,FJohn Loughrey said: "There are many
OL,7,Fmany families who are in a similar
OL,8,Fsituation to us, and because of the
OL,9,Flegacy act, may never get the
OL,10,Fopportunity we've had."
OL,12,FIn two days time families will find
OL,13,Fout if their fight against the
OL,14,Fgovernment controversial legacy
OL,15,Flegislation has been successful.JThis
OL,16,Fcase a reminder that a line in the
OL,17,Fsand simply can't be drawn.
